      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your words paint a harrowing image of grief, but please know that pain is a profound testament to your capacity to feel and love deeply. While the darkness feels overwhelming right now, hope often comes in the quietest moments when we are least expecting it. Would you like to explore ways to find even a small glimmer of light or speak about what brought you to this place tonight?",
