      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "I hear the overwhelming exhaustion in your words, and I want you to know that your pain is valid even when it feels like there is no way out. Please consider that seeking the quiet rest you describe is a way to stop yourself from hurting—and it is possible to ask for help rather than bear this alone. If you can, please reach out to a crisis line or trusted person today; you do not have to navigate this darkness in silence.",
